Description:

  Create a scaffold to implement a simple_generator. It creates the following code:

  controller code: app/generators/NAME/generator.rb
  public partials: app/generators/NAME/views/_show.html.erb
  ubiquo partials: app/generators/NAME/views/ubiquo/_form.html.erb
  component class: app/models/NAME.rb

Examples:

  script/generate simple_generator key:string description:text is_active:boolean
